ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectCanada-Kingdom of Spain - Protocol Amending the Convention for the Avoidance of Double Taxation and the Prevention of Fiscal Evasion with respect to Taxes on Income and on Capital ** CONVENTION **
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, or to delegate powers to sign, on behalf of Canada, subject to ratification, the Protocol between the Government of Canada and the Government of the KINGDOM OF SPAIN Amending the CONVENTION between Canada and SPAIN for the AVOIDANCE OF DOUBLE TAXATION AND THE PREVENTION OF FISCAL EVASION WITH RESPECT TO TAXES ON INCOME AND CAPITAL, signed at Ottawa on November 23, 1976.
